content:
For the Shattered Relics League tutor, see League Tutor (Shattered Relics League).
 Leagues Tutor was removed after an update.
As the contents of this page no longer exist in Old School RuneScape, this article is preserved for historical purposes.
Leagues Tutor
Released14 November 2019 (Update)

Sells itemsLeagues Reward Shop

ExamineHe can tell you all about Leagues.
Map
Advanced data
NPC ID315,316

The Leagues Tutor was an non-player character found in the Lumbridge Castle courtyard. He ran the Leagues Reward Shop for the duration of the Twisted League and the Trailblazer League until the release of the Shattered Relics League.

Dialogue[edit | edit source]

This article on an NPC has an associated dialogue page.
Click here for a transcript of possible conversations with this NPC.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
19 January 2022
(update)

The Leagues Tutor has been replaced by the League Tutor with the release of the Shattered Relics League.

5 November 2020
(update)

The Leagues Tutor now wears the extradimensional bag.

28 October 2020
(update)

With the launch of Trailblazer League, the Leagues Tutor's Relic Hunter outfit has been changed, and has been relocated from Kourend Castle to Lumbridge Castle.
